Looking at the docs for setReuseAddress it looks like it needs to be set before the socket is bound to guarantee it works.  So we'd have to do something like:




        Suggested change











                try (final DatagramSocket datagramSocket = new DatagramSocket(port)) {



                  datagramSocket.setReuseAddress(true);



                try (final DatagramSocket datagramSocket = new DatagramSocket()) {



                  datagramSocket.setReuseAddress(true);



                  datagramSocket.bind(new InetSocketAddress(port));






and the same above for TCP.

